FAQ

Q: Can I use this for my own restaurant?
A: Yes. Self-hosting for your own restaurant (non-production SaaS) is allowed.

Q: Can I build a competing SaaS product with this code?
A: No. You need a commercial license to offer this as a service, resell it,
or embed it into a competing product.

Q: When does this become fully open-source?
A: On 2030-03-19 this version converts to the Apache 2.0 License.

Q: How do I get a commercial license?
A: Contact tiago@tiagoia.dev for commercial licensing terms.
